"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月11日消息，彭博大宗商品高级策略师Mike McGlone认为，通货紧缩可能会在明年取代通货膨胀。大宗商品见顶和美国国债长期债券收益率下降表明，2022年通货紧缩力量有可能重振，这将对[比特币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)和黄金产生积极影响。比特币将有望达到10万美元，而黄金交易价格将达到2000美元。\",\"timestamp\":1639314211,\"title\":\"彭博分析师：通货紧缩将帮助比特币价格在2022年达到10万美元\"},\"digest\":\"WcZU7T0Q26RoE1zjOhYnAUZ7FCG_Zaw95qC6eJdoR2Y\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xA2C43effB0ca850D49EBE026BfbF75F0D99EC7Db\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"KO_9sLNq9YudrQBvbk3tekakqKVG5WroeGIv78sPTdw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"exmv8y4vA2Tp5i3-JzlpViByvUm_F54XbQCS9JQFkB4\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"1UgvTOKVPdJPDhXsm9hHqKYEwE_rDwncBUsZ1l9WTjsyg9Wf1uulGeTR7MCpTwB5JJmS3PWH3JlTv7-DDr1ZWg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xda0247473e243e066bbf758da7c33730ae9d11ffc60af69e58418f474638cb9b2d07043ced6694bc5855904c7a248dfef3d6905d862c41baf0f2d51787fe76441b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"KO_9sLNq9YudrQBvbk3tekakqKVG5WroeGIv78sPTdw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"exmv8y4vA2Tp5i3-JzlpViByvUm_F54XbQCS9JQFkB4\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"WcZU7T0Q26RoE1zjOhYnAUZ7FCG_Zaw95qC6eJdoR2Y\"}"